name: Dancing In The Moonlight
description:
This work is indicative of a particular style of my early drawings 

Towards the beginning of the pandemic drawing was a great release for me

These works, hand drawn were often non-objective doodles (hence my Instagram name) 

These works to me seem to represent feelings, scenes, and emotions which exists between cosmic planes

This one is particularly meaningful to me as it is one of my wife's favorites
